				>
			</end-paragraph>
			<marker class="begin-verse" mid="v24050029">
			</marker>
			<begin-paragraph class="extra-space">
			</begin-paragraph>
			<verse num="29">
				<crossref let="l" cid="c24050029.1">
				</crossref>
				<q class="continue-double" qid="" from="" to="">
				</q>
				Summon archers against Babylon, all those who bend the bow. 
				<crossref let="l" cid="c24050029.2">
				</crossref>
				Encamp around her; let no one escape. 
				<crossref let="m" cid="c24050029.3">
				</crossref>
				Repay her according to her deeds; do to her according to all that she has done. For she has 
				<crossref let="n" cid="c24050029.4">
				</crossref>
				proudly defied the 
				<span class="divine-name">
					Lord
				</span>
				, the Holy One of Israel.
